    "From the histogram in Fig. 12, the distribution of the five emotion scores does not have much difference between the two types of sexual harassment.",
    "However, the most significant observation is the distribution of Fear emotion, where there is a higher distribution of physical sexual harassment than the non-physical sexual harassment sentences at the right side of the chart.",
    "This gives the insight that physical sexual harassment contributed to more fear emotion compared to non-physical sexual harassment.",
    "The insights from the sentiment and emotion analysis are:",
    "Most of sexual harassment is related to negative sentiment, whereas physical sexual harassment contributes to a higher intensity of negative sentiment compared to non-physical sexual harassment. 2."
